Package universum.studios.android.setting.key

Groups classes that may be used for purpose of modification of keys associated with shared preferences.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    KeyModificator
    A simple interface of which implementations may be used to modify keys associated with shared preferences.
    PreferenceKeyModificator
    A simple interface of which implementations may be used to modify keys of Preference instances.
    PreferenceScreenKeyModificator
    A simple interface of which implementations may be used to modify keys of Preference instances associated with PreferenceScreen.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SimplePreferenceKeyModificator
    A simple implementation of PreferenceKeyModificator that uses KeyModificator supplied to SimplePreferenceKeyModificator.SimplePreferenceKeyModificator(KeyModificator) constructor to perform modification of key for any preference passed to SimplePreferenceKeyModificator.modifyKey(Preference).
    SimplePreferenceScreenKeyModificator
    A simple implementation of PreferenceScreenKeyModificator that uses PreferenceKeyModificator supplied to SimplePreferenceScreenKeyModificator.SimplePreferenceScreenKeyModificator(PreferenceKeyModificator) constructor to perform modification of preference's key for all preferences associated with preference screen passed to SimplePreferenceScreenKeyModificator.modifyKeys(PreferenceScreen).
